CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Netskope is known as a Secure Access Service Edge (SASE) provider. It offers cybersecurity for an enterprise's cloud infrastructure, with such products as secure web gateways and firewall as a service. The company's main competitors are Zscaler and Palo Alto Networks.
